cale quantum\ncritical behaviors appear at nonzero temperatures and with external magnetic\nfield near such quantum phase transitions. We discuss the implication of these\nresults to the experiments on Pr$_2$Ir$_2$O$_7$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Oct 2018 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Apr 2019 10:41:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-01"}
