fic angular momentum distributions of the DM halo will generalize the\ndependence of DM response on the halo spin and important implications for\ndirect detection of DM and that of the associated stellar tracers, such as\nstreamers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Oct 2018 18:00:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Aug 2019 19:31:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
