 depths with simulations, as well as\nwith experiments on MNIST and CIFAR-10\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Nov 2018 09:58:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Nov 2018 11:39:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-03"}
