ction can be\ncontrolled to tune the BE within a large window of ~1.5 eV. The experiment also\nreveals that a maximum of 50% coverage can be achieved for chemisorption. In\nthe presence of water, the activated carbonate complex forms a bicarbonate\ncomplex by overcoming a potential barrier of ~0.9 eV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Nov 2018 12:28:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Nov 2018 03:30:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-05"}
