 whether they are modularity based or not, indicating its strong\ntransferability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Nov 2018 15:24:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Nov 2018 00:47:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 11 Nov 2018 07:29:16 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 5 May 2019 12:22:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-07"}
